    description: "I believe in supporting local. That's why I focus exclusively on helping small businesses in west Houston compete and thrive in the digital landscape.",
  },
];

/**
 * Fun facts to add personality
 */
const funFacts = [
  "I've visited every coffee shop within 5 miles of the Energy Corridor (research, of course!)",
  "Weekend mornings usually find me at Terry Hershey Park",
  "Die-hard Texans fan - yes, even through the tough seasons",
  "Self-taught coder who built my first website at age 15",
];
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Meet the team behind Houston Web Services. Based in West Houston's Energy Corridor, we bring 8+ years of web design expertise to help local businesses succeed online."
  openGraph={{
    type: 'profile',
  }}
  jsonLd={{
    type: 'AboutPage',
    name: 'About Houston Web Services',
    description: 'Learn about the experience, expertise, and local commitment behind Houston Web Services - your west Houston web design partner.',
  }}
>
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="about-hero" aria-labelledby="about-hero-heading">
      <div class="about-hero__container">
        <span class="about-hero__eyebrow">About Us</span>
        <h1 id="about-hero-heading" class="about-hero__title">
          Your West Houston<br />Web Partner
        </h1>
        <p class="about-hero__subtitle">
          Building beautiful, effective websites for local businesses since 2016.
          We're not just developers — we're your neighbors.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Personal Introduction Section -->
    <section class="about-intro" aria-labelledby="about-intro-heading">
      <div class="about-intro__container">
        <div class="about-intro__content">
          <div class="about-intro__photo-wrapper">
            <!-- Professional Photo Placeholder -->
            <div class="about-intro__photo" role="img" aria-label="Professional headshot of the Houston Web Services founder">
              <svg class="about-intro__photo-placeholder" viewBox="0 0 200 200" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
                <rect width="200" height="200" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.1"/>
                <circle cx="100" cy="70" r="35" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
                <ellipse cx="100" cy="160" rx="55" ry="40" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.2"/>
              </svg>
              <span class="about-intro__photo-label">Photo Coming Soon</span>
            </div>
            <div class="about-intro__badge">
              <span class="about-intro__badge-text">Est. 2016</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="about-intro__text">
            <h2 id="about-intro-heading" class="about-intro__heading">
              Hi, I'm James — and I'm Passionate About Helping Local Businesses Succeed Online
            </h2>

            <div class="about-intro__bio">
              <p>
                When I started Houston Web Services back in 2016, I had one simple goal: to give small businesses
                in my community the same quality web presence that big corporations enjoy, but with the personal
                attention and care that only a local partner can provide. As a west Houston resident for over a
                decade, I've watched our neighborhoods grow and evolve — from the bustling Energy Corridor to the
                family-friendly streets of Katy and the established charm of Memorial.
              </p>

              <p>
                My journey into web development started long before it became my career. As a teenager, I was
                fascinated by how websites could connect people and ideas. That curiosity led me through years of
                self-study, professional certifications, and hands-on experience with businesses of all sizes.
                But what I discovered along the way is that my real passion isn't just building websites — it's
                helping local business owners like you turn their digital presence into a powerful tool for growth.
              </p>

              <p>
                Today, I've had the privilege of working with over 150 businesses right here in the greater
                Houston area. From the restaurant owner who needed online ordering capabilities to the law firm
                seeking better local visibility, each project has reinforced my belief that great web design
                combined with genuine understanding of local needs creates something truly special. When you
                work with me, you're not getting an outsourced agency — you're getting a neighbor who genuinely
                cares about your success.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-intro__cta">
              <Button
                text="Let's Talk About Your Project"
                href="/contact"
                variant="primary"
                size="large"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Achievements Stats Section -->
    <section class="about-stats" aria-labelledby="about-stats-heading">
      <div class="about-stats__container">
        <h2 id="about-stats-heading" class="sr-only">Our Achievements in Numbers</h2>
        <div class="about-stats__grid">
          {achievements.map((stat) => (
            <div class="about-stats__item">
              <span class="about-stats__number">{stat.number}</span>
              <span class="about-stats__label">{stat.label}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills & Expertise Section -->
    <section class="about-skills" aria-labelledby="about-skills-heading">
      <div class="about-skills__container">
        <div class="about-skills__header">
          <h2 id="about-skills-heading" class="about-skills__title">
            Skills & Expertise
          </h2>
          <p class="about-skills__subtitle">
            Over the years, I've developed a comprehensive skill set tailored specifically to help
            local businesses compete effectively in the digital landscape.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-skills__grid">
          {skillCategories.map((category) => (
            <div class="about-skills__category">
              <h3 class="about-skills__category-title">{category.title}</h3>
              <ul class="about-skills__list" role="list">
                {category.skills.map((skill) => (
                  <li class="about-skills__item">
                    <span class="about-skills__item-name">{skill.name}</span>
                    <span class="about-skills__item-years">{skill.years}+ years</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Community & Personal Touch Section -->
    <section class="about-community" aria-labelledby="about-community-heading">
      <div class="about-community__container">
        <div class="about-community__header">
          <h2 id="about-community-heading" class="about-community__title">
            Rooted in West Houston
          </h2>
          <p class="about-community__subtitle">
            I'm more than just a web developer — I'm a proud member of the west Houston community.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-community__grid">
          {communityHighlights.map((item) => (
            <article class="about-community__card">
              <div class="about-community__icon" aria-hidden="true" set:html={item.icon} />
              <h3 class="about-community__card-title">{item.title}</h3>
              <p class="about-community__card-text">{item.description}</p>
            </article>
          ))}
        </div>

        <!-- Fun Facts -->
        <div class="about-funfacts">
          <h3 class="about-funfacts__title">A Few Fun Facts</h3>
          <ul class="about-funfacts__list" role="list">
            {funFacts.map((fact) => (
              <li class="about-funfacts__item">
                <span class="about-funfacts__bullet" aria-hidden="true">☕</span>
                {fact}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="about-cta" aria-labelledby="about-cta-heading">
      <div class="about-cta__container">
        <h2 id="about-cta-heading" class="about-cta__title">
          Ready to Work with a Local Expert?
        </h2>
        <p class="about-cta__description">
          Let's sit down — virtually or at your favorite west Houston coffee shop — and discuss
          how we can help your business grow online. The first consultation is always free.
        </p>
        <div class="about-cta__buttons">
          <Button
            text="Schedule a Free Consultation"
            href="/contact"
            variant="primary"
            size="large"
          />
          <Button
            text="View My Work"
            href="/portfolio"
            variant="secondary"
            size="large"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* =================================================================
   * HERO SECTION
   * ================================================================= */
  .about-hero {
    padding: var(--spacing-20) var(--spacing-4) var(--spacing-16);
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--color-primary-50) 0%,
      var(--color-background) 100%
    );
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-hero__container {
    max-width: var(--container-4xl);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-hero__eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-semibold);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--letter-spacing-wider);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);
  }

